{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十八回 往事如烟\n\n本章主要讲述辛捷追上方少魌后，在岩洞中与方少魌重逢。方少魌向辛捷讲述了自己投江后的经历：被渔妇救起，与金欹重逢，金欹为她划伤自己脸部，最终两人在荒僻岩区隐居。辛捷得知方少魌已嫁金欹，心中百感交集。\n\n与此同时，恒河三佛与金鲁厄追踪而至。辛捷利用洞穴地形和阵法困住金鲁厄，并与金伯胜夷打赌，若一掌击不倒辛捷，恒河三佛将永不再履中原。章末辛捷让方少魌带金欹逃离，自己面对恒河三佛的挑战。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹！难道不能给我解释的机会吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "辛大侠一路跟来作甚？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你——你没有什么对不住我的，也没有什么要我谅解的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是谁？看来受伤很重，让我帮你将他医好吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹！你……你……唉！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捷哥！捷哥！为什么又让我碰见你呢？……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金欹！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是金欹？'天魔'金欹？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捷哥！你不能……我不许你伤他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还好，伤得不甚重，大概再休息个把时辰即可以清醒过来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想不到我会嫁给他是吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道那天我投江后……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！捷哥……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龄姐姐如何了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龄姐姐",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那天我投水以后，我恨一切，我也恨我自己，于是我屏住气拼命要往水下钻，想让江水将我淹没，永远淹没，但是浪是如此大，我支持不了几口气即昏绝过去——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奶奶！那位姑姑就在那边！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "乖孩子，你先跑去看看，不要让这可怜的人冻坏了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奶奶！她已经醒了，啊，你看她全身都湿透丁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！小福真亏了你的……姑娘！你感觉好吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你漂到什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当时我也不知道，后来听那救我的渔妇说，才知竟是距离武汉百余里的",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你命运比我还好些……唉！我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捷哥，别想以前了吧！让我告诉你以后的事情——",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "归宿",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样过了近半年，我对一切俱灰心了，我的感情像槁木般永远死沉过去，但一个人的命运并不如此地简单……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还记得那天下午，本是初春奔放时节，突然……突然金欹来了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来清静而恬淡的小茅屋——渔妇的家，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一日我正在陪那好心的渔妇做女红……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呼！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开门！魌妹出来！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天魔金欹",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金欹",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹……魌妹！你害得我好苦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金欹！你给我滚！滚得远远的，我永远不要再见到你……再见到你们两人——",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我恨……我恨你们两人……啊！金欹你！你怎么了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹我……我内伤发了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你一定很恨我，恨我的为人……但是……但是我愿意为你改过自新的，你知道我是多么的爱你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好吧！我不敢勉强你，虽然这不是我以往的作风。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方少魌继续对辛捷说：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你这恶魔！你连父母都能杀，我还敢喜欢你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "逆子！你这杀亲的逆子！你这不容宽恕的逆子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹！当年我犯了滔天大错不容宽谅，但你说的话可算数？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "划吧！划吧！我要看看能杀父母的人能不能划自己的脸？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！方少魌你作了什么事啊？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "于是我又开始流浪了……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "安静点！慢慢讲！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后来我在江湖上流浪，闻得七妙神君要到泰山参加大会，我早已怀疑'七妙神君'必是你，所以我无法自主地向山东方向行去……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等我达到泰山脚下时，大会已经作鸟兽散，但我突然发现了金欹，他又是伤得这般重，从岩石边爬上来，殷红的刀痕仍醒目地交叉着……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹，宽恕我！魌妹，再别离开我！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至此我感情完全崩溃了，怜惜他的心情使我变成爱他的痴心，于是我带着他来了此处，这荒凉无人的岩区，永远离开人群，孤单终其一生……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你怎会被'恒河三佛'追上呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不是他！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说在洞里呆得烦了，要出去散散心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁知竟碰着那三个老鬼，还有他们那讨厌的徒弟……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错！那三人徒弟叫'金鲁厄'，他对你怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这家伙不是好东西，如果落在我手上非将他碎尸万段！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁叫你长得这么漂亮呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啐",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这家伙是蛤蟆想——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹！魌妹！水！水！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看！雄天鹅醒了呢！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_shao_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方少魌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你瞧！这就是那最高大的老头子打伤的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹，你听脚步声！是'恒河三佛'等来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恒河三佛",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹！随我来！咱们可得为他们准备些东西，免得这些夷族笑我中原无物……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恒河三佛",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金鲁厄",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等下捉着那姑娘，请师父饶她一命吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "摩诘拉诃，孚罗，阿隆黎！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们必定在这儿",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蛮夷的尊客此时才到，辛捷已遥候多时。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天竺",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恒河三佛",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子！有种的给老子滚出来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个蛮子，原来你到中国就只学会这几句骂人的话！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恒河三佛",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓辛的出来，咱们再战三百回合。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要我出来不难，不过你们'恒河三佛'说话算不算数？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金鲁厄，你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lu_e",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然也一样！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼！假如真个如此，莫说一句，咱们十句也听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十句",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lu_e",
      "speaker_name": "金鲁厄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……哦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你们得听我一言，咱们中国武技上虽胜不了你们蛮子许多，但",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "归元古阵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恒河三佛",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七妙神君",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "色",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "归元古阵",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恒河三佛",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三个老糊涂，你们的乖徒儿别想出来了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恒河三佛",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好狂妄的口气，我辛某不才，尚还不在乎大师一掌呢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此话当真？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "魌妹！将那人带出来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
